OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMicrosoft splits Teams and 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FOffice globally            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Microsoft has said it is splitting the 
OL,6, Teams business messaging and video app 
OL,7, from its Office software globally.     
OL,9,FThe firm separated the two products in 
OL,10,FEurope last year as it faced a possible
OL,11,Ffine from competition watchdogs.       
OL,13,FTeams was added to Office in 2017. The 
OL,14,FEuropean Commission has been           
OL,15,Finvestigating the move after a         
OL,16,Fcomplaint from rival Slack in 2020.    
OL,18,FA Microsoft spokesperson told the BBC  
OL,19,Fthat the move is to "ensure clarity for
OL,20,Four customers".                        
